name: The Red Castle
location: 6 2nd Alley, Sanmin Street, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Coffee and Fine Dining in a Colonial BuildingThe Red Castle is over 100 years old. It was built in 1899 and used to belong to shipping company millionaire Yi Lee. In 2000, it was refitted to become a restaurant. The exterior is built with red bricks and arched corridors. This is the building’s unique structure.

name: Feng Hua Restaurant
location: No.209, Sec. 2, Shuangshi Rd., ,  220, Taiwan, Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: With clean and quiet environment, modern and Zen style, the restaurant mainly offers Jiangsu and Zhejiang Cuisine. The famous food are Baked Shallot Chop, Wuxi Chop, Radish Beef and others. You would never want to miss the surprised daily cold meats.

name: Hong Kong Chen's gruel and noodle.
location: No.46, Zhulin Rd., ,  234, Taiwan, Yonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Standard Hong Kong style gruel, boil with smal fire for more than 4 hours until the rice becomes soft, and more than 10 kinds of tastes You may enjoy every minute as you eat.

name: Zhening Jia Garden Restaurant
location: No.70, Sec. 1, Zhongshan Rd., ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner has over 30 years of experience preparing authentic Zhejiang and Ningbo dishes. His expertise creates delicious dishes that one will always remember.

name: Fu Zhou Lin Pepper Bun
location: Minsheng St. (inside the Food Street), Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Legend has it that Fu Zhou China's "Green onion meat bun" is actually the ancestor of Taiwan's famous pepper bun, and that explains why Taiwan's pepper buns are filled with large quantities of green onions.

name: China Spice
location: 2nd Floor, No. 1 Section, Wenhua 3rd Road, Linkou District, , Linkou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Serving traditional Jiang-Nan and a perfect mixture with local cuisine using only the freshest product to produce a mix of indulgent authentic favourites as well as exciting Chinese fusion dishes.

name: Weng Meiyu Malt
location: Number 128 Sinjhuang Road, , New Taipei, Xinzhuang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The molasses melts in your mouth and the sugary malt aroma holds on the palate for a long time, bringing back childhood memories with the candy. The boss of Weng Meiyu uses traditional method to  create  each  and  every  batch.

name: Osmanthus Farm
location: No.4, Xinxingkeng, , , Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Special Recommendations: Preserved Osmanthus Petals in Ice Sugar, Lotus Root in Preserved Sweet Osmanthus Petals

name: Sanzhi Pigs Light Meal Restaurant
location: No.58-8, Kanzijiao, ,  253, Taiwan, Shimen Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Sanzhi Pigs ran from Sanzhi to Shimen, with cute pig bottoms on the counters. You can also find popular freshly baked cheesecake and toast here.

name: Jiuliaopo Ranch green tea rice
location: No.226, Sec. 1, Dingping Rd., Shihding Dist.,  22342, Taiwan , Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: To taste this dish, you need to add green tea seed oil into freshly made rice and blend well. The taste has a tea fragrance and it is not greasy.

name: Flower fairy cafe'
location: No.53, Guanhai Bivd., Bali Dist  249, Taiwan, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: A large painting by Van Gogh hung on the wall will come into your eyes as soon as you enter the cafe decorated with European style. The dishes offered are a combination of Taiwan ans European styles. It is a good place for relaxation.

name: Jinshan Duck Meat
location: No. 104, jinbauli St., ,  208, Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner insists on using mature ducks farmed for 130 days and demands the preservation of its original flavor in the process of cooking. The ducks sold here are all freshly killed and sold. The delicious duck meat is impressive and memorable.

name: Baoyun Taro Balls shop
location: No.8, Rueifang St., Rueifang Dist.,  22441, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsTofu pudding with taro balls, herbal jelly pudding with taro balls, fresh milk with tofu pudding, tian bu laBaoyun is the name of a 97-year-old grandma who still possesses the beautiful traits of a traditional Taiwanese woman.

name: Feng Wei Pork thick soup
location: Minsheng St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Towards the end of the 1960's, Ruifang and the nearby Houtong area were prosperous mining towns. The 1st-generation boss of "Feng Wei Pork thick soup" came from Sandiaoling and decided to settle down in Ruifang. Utilizing his culinary skills garnered from a stint in a big city hotel, he saw the potential of pork thick soup in the Ruifang market.

name: Liao Mucheng Century-Old Shop One-Bite Cake
location: No.129, Jishan St., Rueifang Dist.,  22448, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsDifferent flavors of one-bite cakes and spring field pizza (available in winter only)The one-bite cake has different names in Chinese, including cake dumpling, dragon cake, or mille feuille (one thousand layers). It is a kind of moon cake-like Taiwanese cake with either sweet or salty stuffing.

name: Fuchang Shop(Tea Leaf pork meatball Soup)
location: No.18, Pinglin St., , , Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Another Pinglin specialty is tea leaf pork meatball soup. First, the tea leaves used areis selected and grounded into a fine powder, then it is added to top quality minced pork. Aficionados say the two ingredients make a perfect pair. The finished tea leaf pork meatballs have a unique texture that is crispy and springy, and the taste is more refreshing and less oily than traditional pork...

name: Mountain Legends
location: No.51, Fengge St., ,  222, Taiwan, Shenkeng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Culinary art knows no boundaries. It is an ulimate enjoyment to savor delicious dishes in the natural environment of Shenkeng. Steaks, BBQ, buﬀets or outdoor karaoke and party food are all the delicacies to please the eyes and mouths.

name: Jinshan Chongyu Restaurant
location: No.203, Zhongshcn Rd., ,  208, Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The first rolled pastry and meat pastry shop on Jinshan Street, this restaurant offers juicy pork and beef pastries, a delicacy widely acclaimed by those who have tasted it. The specially made salted chicken, pickled cabbage, and ferns are all very tasty as well.

name: Yingge Xiangxiang Dumpling Shop
location: No.37 Nanya Rd., ,  239 Taiwan, Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The big, delicious handmade dumplings here are ﬁlled with fresh leeks and pork.：

name: She's Green Mussel
location: No.22, Duchuantou St., ,  249, Taiwan, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The store has a history of 20 years. Green Mussel and various seashell food and other dishes are served for your choice.Green Mussel and friend beef with onion are specially recommeded.

name: Juisanfuli Restaurant
location: No. 45 Houtong Road, Houtong Borough, Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsSesame Chicken, Steamed Silky Fowl, Fujian Shark’s Fin Soup (Buddha Jumps Over the Wall), and Winter Melon Soup with ScallopAs to what the restaurant's name suggests, it was the employee's restaurant of Juisan Mining. During the Japanese colonial period, it was called Juisan Dining Hall. After the restoration of Taiwanese rule, it was renamed as Juisanfuli Restaurant.

name: Baoan Medicine
location: 89 Zhongzheng Road, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Three Generations of Herbal MedicineWalking  along  Tamsui Old Street, there is a shop filled with herbal medicine and  Buddhist  statues.  This  is the  100-year-old  Baoan  Medicine shop,which has been run for three generations. It is known as being the oldest medicine shop in Tamsui and Bali. They use decent materials to make health drinks.

name: New Harbor Sea Food
location: No.60, Xingang St., ,  228, Taiwan, Gongliao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Over 40 years old, New Harbor Sea Food is one of the oldest restaurants in AoDi. Constantly introducing new dishes, the restaurant is highly popular. Sweet-and-sour eels and stirred-fried abalones are both signature dishes.

name: Red Vermicelli
location: No. 22-5, Section 1, Baoan Street, Shulin District, , Shulin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Handmade, colorful darker shade noodles are heated then carefully boiled so they remain firm, and simmered, braised chitterling is added that leaves people coming back for more.

name: Shifang Tea Cuisine
location: No. 92, Shuiliujiao Rd., ,  232, Taiwan, Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner uses the zen-style of Japan’s Kaiseki cuisine in the dishes oﬀered in the store. There are over a hundred dishes that change with the seasons for the tourists to choose from.

name: Tofu & Old Mansion
location: No.140, Shenkeng St., ,  222, Taiwan, Shenkeng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: There are many posters of old Taiwanese movies and newspaper clips on the wall. This nostalgic restaurant oﬀers a clean and bright environment. The signature dishes are Beef & Sinky Tofu, Spicy Duck Blood Tofu Soup and braised bamboo shoots cooked with chicken broth and pork.

name: Fu Gu Beef Noodles
location: No.21, Minsheng St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: If the number of customers in a shop is an indication of the shop's popularity, then any shop that has customers "anytime" or "always" must be considered a good shop. Right around the corner in front of Rui Fang Train Station, there stands a three-window storefront. The store is always teeming with customers slurping the store's famous beef noodles.

name: Gao's Fried Fresh Squid
location: No.28, Gongkou Street, , , Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: A full bowl of fried fresh squid contains only two simple food ingredients, cabbage and squid; the aromatic fried cabbage has a crunchy texture and tastes sweet as well as the well-processed squid is crusty and chewy. Mixed with 4 seasonings, sour, sweet, salty, and spicy, the simple bowl of squid becomes very special.

name: Fumei Croissant Bakery
location: No. 25 Sinyi Street, Sanxia Town, Taipei County, Sanxia Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The bona fide gift item to bring back from a trip to Sanxia is dozen or so Croissant (literally in Mandarin "bull horns"). Tucked away in a lonely little alcove of Sanxia Market is Fumei Croissant Bakery-the ﬁrst shop to create the recipe for "golden croissants". They have a tender middle and a crispy exterior and taste buttery and by that virtue sell so well.

name: Yaomei Agricultural Product Shop
location: No.146, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsAlishan High-Mountain Tea, Handmade NougatA few steps from the intersection of Shuqi Road and Jishan Street, there is a log signboard reading (Yao Mei A Li Shan Wu Long Cha), Jiufen Yaomei Agricultural Product Shop. When turning to the other side of the signborad, a small aluminum doorplate from grandpa's time is spotted.

name: Wu Mama Handmade Dumplings
location: Floor 2, No. 212, Chuanxing Road, Taishan District, , Taishan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: When you visit Taishan you can find many inexpensive snacks. Although most are common, their preparation requires meticulous care. One well-known stand that serves fresh dumplings fitting this description is located on the second floor of the Taishan Public Market. The dumplings are highly praised, and customers often buy many boxes at a time.

name: Jiufen Food Quiz Shop
location: No. 106, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productsfirst stinky tofu shop in Jiufen, bamboo rice, Taiwanese proverbsJiufen Food Quiz Shop was the first stinky tofu shop ever in Jiufen. Dozens of Taiwanese proverbs are posted on the walls as a way for customers to learn more about traditional Taiwanese wisdom.

name: Pizza Olmo
location: No.46, Zhibo Rd., ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The secret to wood-smoked pizza is the kiln built by the owner himself, with longan wood as fuel. The fruit scent add to the taste and crunchiness of pizza.

name: Lee Noodles
location: No. 404 Jinsin Street, Zhonghe  Dis t.,  New Taipei  City, Zhonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Take a left turn after you head out of Lane 410 and you'll see Lee Noodles about 50 m down the road. They are known for the way they cut the noodles. As they busily prepare the meals, you can see how the division of labor works. Some prepare ingredients, some cut them and some stir fry them.

name: A-Po Sashimi
location: No. 63 Zhongjheng First Road, Yingge Town, Taipei County, Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: A-Po Sashimi is a representative of the finest seafood available in Yingge. The place is always packed causing trafﬁc jams in Zhongjheng First Road. There is not a lot of variety on the menu with items such as Taiwanese style sashimi rolls that go well with a bowl of fresh miso soup. If that is not enough to eat, you can add some snack plates and refreshing chilled noodles.

name: Ching Ching Restaurant
location: No.6, Sec. 3, Zhongyang Rd., , , Tucheng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Chef’s Specials: Shrimp Cake, Tomato Soup in Pork Rib Broth

name: Shiding Lindera Sausages
location: No.6, Xiahengping, ,  223, Taiwan, Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: “Lindera” is a kind of wild pepper spice. Hind leg meat of black pigs is used for a  ﬁrm taste, and the light lemon scent has a bit of lemongrass and ginger.

name: Old Friends Sweet Taro Ball
location: No. 4-3, Jishan St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productshandmade sweet taro ball, ginger tea sweet taro ball, mountain yam sweet taro ball, green tea sweet taro ballThere is a prominent yellow signboard which reads "Old Friends Sweet Taro Balls" not far from the entrance of Jishan Old Street (Jiudaoko), approximately 20 meters to the right.The Old Friends Sweet Taro Ball was founded in 1990.

name: De-li Service Station(Soy-Stewed Pork Knuckles)
location: No.140, Shuiliujiao Road, , , Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Pinglin is a popular destination for cyclists and walkers because it offers a great environment for outdoor activities. When people are done with these exercises, they need good tasting food that can replenish their lost energy and fill their appetite. At moments like these, Soy-Stewed Pork Knuckle is a dish that cannot be missed.

name: “Healthful＂ crisp roll
location: No.19, Touqian Rd., ,  242, Taiwan, Xinzhuang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner of this shop tasted the custard crisp roll by accident when he was abroad. Since then he couldn't forget the taste. Then he began to do some research and invented the delicious “Healthful” crisp roll. There are six ﬂavors; people just couldn't help eaing one by one because it is so delicious.

name: Camellia Village herbal ice cream
location: No.67, Meizhuxi, ,  227, Taiwan, Shuangxi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Four ﬂavors of herbal ice cream are provided for the customers to choose from: ginger  ﬂower, lavender, sunﬂower and rosemary.

name: Xiaode Zhang Niuweng Mutton stove
location: No.89, Sec. 1, Zhongshan Rd., ,  234, Taiwan, Yonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Chip mutton into small pieces, add red date, medlar and other 28 Chinese herbs, and stew with charcoal fire for more than 2 hours. The soup is sweet and nutritious; the mutton is tender and inexhaustible after taste.

name: Original Flavor Sesame Chicken
location: No. 56-3 Zhongyang North Road, Sanchong District, Taipei County, Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: If you were to compare all the fine snack foods of Sanchong, no doubtthe sesame oil chicken would be on the top of the list. Original Flavor Sesame Chicken are prepared every afternoon, but it isn’t merely the freshness that wins favor, but also the price, which is more reasonable than similar shops.

name: Taishan Li’s pepper pie shop
location: No.216, Sec. 2, Tailin Rd., ,  243, Taiwan, Taishan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The shop is very small with only 6-7 square meters. The two big jars for baking the pepper pie are made by hand by the boss himself with volcanic earth. The pepper pie has a taste of crisp, but is not greasy with very thin skin and big meat stuffing. The stuffing is made of pig’s fresh rear leg meat plus green onion, pepper and fragrance made by private secrete formula.

name: Jinshan Temple Gate Ice City
location: No.94, jinbauli St., ,  208,Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner has worked very hard to develop new products. He is concerned about the selection of ingredients and believes in the business principle of making and selling fresh items. There are dozens of ice dishes, among which the "fluffy ice" is most loved by customers.

name: Yongbo Garbage Noodles
location: No. 157, Zhongzheng First Road, Yingge District, , Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: One of the most unusual places to eat in Yingge is at an inexpensive restaurant well-known among locals, Yongbo Garbage Noodles. The strange name of these noodles comes from the turbid nature of the soup base, which is made by simmering pork bone and then adding a special spicy oil.

name: Sanzhi Happy Pig Bakery
location: No.27, Puwei, ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: In the bakery are many pig decoraions, even the exterior of the counter hasconcrete pig botoms. The bakery uses imported cream, cheese, buter, and ﬂourto make breads and cakes with a true sense of happiness.

name: Chen’s Tofu Dessert
location: Mon. ~ Fri. 10:00-17:00 /Weekend 09:30-18:30, Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The tofu desserts here use Wang’s Tofu as the main ingredient, which include products such as tofu ice cream, tofu cake, tofu cheese, and tofu pudding. Various fragrant and delicious tofu desserts can be found here.：

name: Tea Country Garden
location: No. 90, Shuiliujiao Rd., ,  232, Taiwan, Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: This place offers many kinds of tea snacks, and this is also Pinglin’s biggest tea snack shop that produces items such as tea egg rolls, teacakes, square tea biscuits, tea cakes, and tea candies.Tea Leaf Egg RollsCooking in Pinglin often involves infusing traditional dishes with local tea, which makes the food particularly popular among tourists who want to try something new.

name: Tofu Ice Cream
location: No.48, Shenkeng St., ,  222, Taiwan, Shenkeng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Dexing Residence is the inventor of tofu ice cream. With a slight touch of scorching aroma, tofu ice cream is creamy and smooth. It comes with a variety of ﬂavors, while tofu, caramel and sesame are more popular. The comic books and postcards drawn by Teacher Yen Song-Tao are also available for sale.

name: Shunyi Tea House
location: No. 216, Sec. 8, Beiyi Rd., ,  232, Taiwan , Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Famous for the specially made tea dishes. Their tea oil noodle has a light teafragrance that spreads in your mouth.

name: Jiufen Zheng’s Traditional Fishballs
location: No.25, Jishan St., Rueifang Dist.,  22448, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productstraditional fishball, cuttlefish ball, Fuzhou ball, braised pork rice, specialty dry noodlesZheng's Traditional Fishballs is located in the first half of Jishan Old Street, and has been established for more than a decade. The name of this restaurant demonstrates its confidence in their brand and quality.

name: Mountain and Sea View Teahouse
location: No. 150, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productsscenic view, beverages, tea ceremony, set mealsThe Mountain and Sea View Teahouse resides in a yellow tiled three-story building near the rear of Jishan St. As the location happens to be where the Old Street takes a turn, with the Rear Viewing Platform, this teahouse has a better, non-obscured view than most.

name: Xiong's baked roll and twisted cruller
location: No.206, Xinzhuang Rd., ,  242, Taiwan, Xinzhuang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: This shop is run by 3 generations in the past 75 years. The baked roll and twisted cruller have accompanied many people as they grow up. Thebaked roll, twisted cruller, bread twist and "twins" are most populaand attract a lot of customers.

name: Miners Café & Restaurant
location: No.8-1, Jinguang Rd., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productsgold, miner’s boxed lunchDuring the Japanese occupation period, Jinguashi was a mining area under the management of a Japanese company, Kamaishi Mining and Iron Works.

name: Hengxi Q Meatballs
location: No. 193 Minsheng Street; Sanxia District, , Sanxia Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Sanxia is a town with a main street feel. As you leave the Sanxia Old Street area where most tourists gather, surrounding it are still many food stalls and eateries waiting for visitors to come have a taste. One of the best is Hengxi Q Meatballs, located on Minsheng Street. Its namesake dish features an outer skin that is chewy while its lean-meat filling has a stark aroma.

name: Fu-Guei-Tao-Yuan Art & Culture
location: No. 96, Chongqing Street, Yingge District, , Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Just like the exhibition hall attached to it, the Fu-Guei restaurant uses valuable artistic pieces by well-known artists for its decorations and serving implements. When eating hot pot served with a dining set that costs over ten thousand Taiwan dollars, the beer- marinated chicken seems even more intoxicating.

name: Old Place
location: No.21, Sec. 2, Danjin Rd., ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Old Place is a very popular restaurant for street-food-type dishes in Sanzhi. The dumplings contain whole shrimp. The shrimp tastes fresh, and the broth is thick. Steamed meat balls from Chaozhou are soft, chewy, but not greasy, with lots of meat inside.

name: Big White Sand
location: No.33-6, Xiayuankeng, ,  253, Taiwan, Shimen Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: This restaurant provides Chinese stir-fry dishes and Western dishes. They also provide a very popular homemade taro dessert. The restaurant offers ice cream in the summer, and this wonderful gesture helps to cool the tourists.

name: Lin Yi-He Hall healthy preserved fruit
location: No.3, Chang’an St., ,  227, Taiwan, Shuangxi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Chinese medicine is used to make all kinds of tasty healthy preserved fruits, such as olives and eight celestial fruit.

name: Shuangxi Delicious Refreshment Room
location: ,  227, Taiwan, Shuangxi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The most well-known bento (lunch box) store in Shuangxi. The smoked pig scalp is highly recommended. According to customers’ preferences, the dish can be prepared differently.

name: Hall of dragon and phoenix pie shop
location: No.49, Zhongzheng Rd., ,  247, Taiwan, Luzhou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Reputed for more than 50 years, the Restaurant has kept sincerity and trust as its operation concepts and followed traditional pie-making process. Its main products are various exquisite pies such as engagement pie, celebration cake and birthday turtle cake, etc. Little Deng pie and Lijun pie, the double glory of Luzhou, are its famous products and have met with great favor.

name: Sisters fritter
location: No. 25,Duchuantou St., ,  249, Taiwan, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The old store has a history of more than 30 years. Besides milk fritter,milk donut, Chinese steamed buns stuffed with pickled vegetable and taro pieetc. are also served. The fritters have crisp skin on the outside and tastes sift and chewing on the inside.

name: Ah Lan Herbal Glutinous Rice Cake
location: No.90, Jishan St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: When tourists visit Jiufen, not only do they want to try the taro balls, they will definitely want to queue up for Ah Lan's herbal glutinous rice cakes! These cakes are another type of delicious food item representative of Jiufen!

name: Jiufen Teahouse
location: No. 142, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productstea, ceramics, painting, historical site, five tael cake, scenic viewThe owner of the Jiufen Teahouse, Zhi-Sheng Hong, came to Jiufen in the 1980s and purchased this old house in 1987. He has preserved most of the original structure, save for one major adjustment: the creation of an open inner courtyard for more natural lighting.

name: Shanquanshui Handmade Bean Curd Tofu Pudding
location: No.149 Minsheng St., Sanxia  Dist.,  237, Taiwan, Sanxia Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: After a trip to the busy market on Sanxia’s Minsheng Street, nothing satisfies the thirsty and weary soul more than a bowl of handmade bean curd made from natural mountain spring water. At the Shanquanshui restaurant desser shop, the bean curd tofu pudding is meticulously prepared to give off a slight aroma that is revealed in the first bite and becomes stronger as one begins to savor th...

name: Jiayi Honey Tea Goose
location: Floor 2, No. 212, Chuanxing Road, Taishan District, , Taishan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: There are many ways to cook goose, with each having its own enthusiasts. One of the more unique styles is Taishan’s honey tea goose. This stand carefully selects mature geese that weigh between 5 to 6 kilograms. After cooking the chef spreads on honey and homemade sauce, letting the flavors penetrate the meat before smoke-roasting the bird.

name: Youngdoor Cafe
location: 29-1 Zhongyi Road, Jinshan District, , Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Can Northern Taiwan look like Greece? Along Provincial Highway No. 2, there is a very Greek-style small restaurant in blue and white with an ocean view called “Youngdoor  Café”. The layout of the cozy interior furnishing makes it comfortable to enjoy the scenic view. Many visitors choose this place to have afternoon tea, or a cup of coffee with some cake or waffles.

name: Yen Yi Te Xing
location: No.48, Shenkeng St.,  Shenkeng  Dist.,  New, Shenkeng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C

name: Smoked Restaurant
location: No.27, Sec. 1, Zhongxing St., ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Taste the pride of Bavaria in Taiwan! Many traditional German dishes are provided here, such as smoked pig’s feet, sausages, smoked poultry, cheese from the Alps, and world-famous HB Beer.

name: Nanshihjiao Taiwan Chilled Doufu
location: Alley 20, Lane 418, Jingxin Street, Zhonghe City, Taipei County, Zhonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: There is a stand that sells chilled doufu (bean curd) half-way in the night market. The purveyor is good with people and her shop selling the sweet desert has been open for many years. All the usual toppingshave been boiled and are ready to eat, but the most commonly ordered treats are peanut and mung bean.

name: Wugu old customer meat bals and oyster noodles
location: No.120, Sec. 1, Minyi Rd., ,  248, Taiwan, Wugu Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Although the shop only sells noodles and meat balls, the boss, nevertheless, pays very much attention to the quality of his products. He makes a set quantity of meat balls everyday, and the sausages are made and sold out the same day. Since the materials are fresh without adding any chemicals and colors, the food is by no means harmful to your health.

name: Five Stars pettitoes rice
location: No.119, Sec. 1, Ziqiang Rd., ,  241, Taiwan, Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: For more than 30 years, the restaurant has been known for its specialty, gravy pettitoes, made by inherited secrete formula. The cooking method pays special attention to whether the greasy and fishy smell is removed, and whether the gravy flavor has deeply penetrated into meat.

name: Master Liang's beef noodle and dumpling
location: No.572, Sec2, Zhongshan Rd., , New Taipei, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The soup of the famous beef noodle is made by beef cooked for a long time, and it also contains the gravy beef shank and hand made noodles, which makes it very chewy and delicious.

name: Badasang aboriginal restaurant
location: No.111, Guanhai Blvd., Bail Dist.,  249, Taiwan, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Badasnag means face tottoo in the language of Taroko Tribe. The exterior of the building is make by natural materials and the food offered in the restaurant is mainly cooked in the aboriginal people's style, a good place to taste new flavours.

name: Bitou A-zhu Seafood Old Restaurant
location: No. 115 Bitou Road, Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: When driving towards Fulong or Yilan along the Coastal Highway, visors will see a huge signboard reading "Bitou A-zhu Seafood Old Restaurant" before entering the Bitou Cape Tunnel. This restaurant founded in 1986 is very famous among connoisseurs.

name: Hot Oil Mochi
location: ,  (No. 44 Store in Food Street), Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: 40 years ago, Grandpa Mochi was not as old as now, so everyone in Rui Fang called him "Uncle Mochi". It was then that Uncle Mochi started his little hot oil mochi store, painstakingly selling the same dish. His mochi warmed the stomachs of many Rui Fang people; they also warmed many Rui Fang people's memories.

name: Lanxiang House
location: No. 173 Jishan Street, Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsWild Red-Core Native Guava, Golden Date, Red Cypress Essential OilPassing by Shanhaiguan Café, a magnificent view come into sight. While enjoying the wide and open scenery of Jiufen, visitors can smell a strong fruit fragrance.

name: Taro Potato Teahouse
location: No.18, Shihsia Ln., Rueifang Dist.,  22448, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Shopping DirectoryPayment Options： Cash,  Credit Card,  Other Information : Will accept foreign currencyRecommended Productsmeal, tea ceremony, dishes for sharing, Jiufen mountain view, antiques, wooden craftsThe Taro Potato Teahouse is located diagonally across from the Jiufen Business District Tourist Information Center on Shuqi Road.

name: Linyuan Jumbo Meatballs
location: No. 104, Fuzhong Road, Banqiao District, , Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Quail’s Eegg, mushroom, and shredder bamboo shoots are mixed with top quality pork and then stuffed into a chewy, handmade wrapping. The finished meatball is topped off with a garlic sauce, completing this wonderful dish.

name: Changying Meatballs
location: No. 35, Xingzheng Road, Yingge District, , Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Traditional Changhua meatballs are also available in Yingge! Hearty meat that borders on addicting is crammed into a chewy, springy dumpling wrapping, resulting in a meatball that is so filling, only one bowl is enough to satisfy your appetite. An important part of good meatballs is the sauce, and at this restaurant a homemade version combined with a small scoop of crushed garlic hits th...

name: BestBrews
location: 1st Floor, No. 1 Section, Wenhua 3rd Road, Linkou District, , Linkou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Meet up with friends or colleagues in the Bar for a refreshing beer from our international Best Brews™ collection.

name: HASEGAWA CO.LTD
location: 10F.-5, No. 14, Ln. 609, Sec. 5, Chongyang Rd., , , Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Leader’s Brown Sugar bubble Tea is a gift box of Brown Sugar Pearl Milk Tea recommended by the most bloggers in 2020.Strictly selected several high-quality Assam black teas, paired with mochi tapioca .100% use Taiwan brown sugar, presenting a rich brown sugar aroma.Perfectly reproduce the deliciousness of Taiwanese hand-rolled bubble tea.Let you easily enjoy the fun of brown sugar pearl ...

name: Sancai Lingzhi Mushroom Emperor Cuisine
location: No.52-1, Shibachong Xi, ,  223, Taiwan (R.O.C.), Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The broth is cooked for two days with precious deer horn , lingzhi mushrooms as well as 30 unique Chinese herbs. It is consumed with delicacies from the mountain, a meal suitable for all seasons.

name: Xiangmao Candy Factory
location: No.91, Shuiliujiao Rd., ,  232, Taiwan, Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Pinglin’s only tea candy factory. Of the six or seven kinds already developed, Qingru tea candy is the most well-known. The reputation of tea nougat is also quite good, as it contains a rich and fragrant taste.

name: Su Yi Xing restaurant
location: No.77, Zhonghua Rd., ,  227, Taiwan, Shuangxi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Deep fried pork and bean sheet shrimp rolls are the most popular dishes. The store owner used to be a singer; thus, sometimes customersmay enjoy music performance while savoring the Shuangxi delicacies.

name: Jinshan Brothers Restaurant
location: No.2, Jinbauli St., ,  208, Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Brothers Restaurant, which is located next to Tzuhu Temple, is run by the three Kuo Brothers who use their outstanding cooking talent to make wonderful dishes. The pan-fried ribs which tastes crispy on the outside and soft on the isnide are the most popular dish.

name: The Dlcservice Cafe
location: No.6, Ln. 167, Jing'an Road, , , Zhonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Located close to the Jing'an MRT Station, the "Dlcservice cafe," which has a country-style decoration at the gate. Once you open the wooden door, the interior decoration gives people a very relaxing feel. There're small objects hanging on the walls, such as postcards and leather accessories. Exactly, it sells Japanese groceries. The decoration setting and the menu are usually changed eve...

name: Teng Feng Fishball Museum
location: 117 Zhongzheng Road, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Lets Learn about All Sorts of FishballsTo help people understand the history of Tamsui fishballs, the Teng Feng Fishball Museum was erected. It is the first Fishball Museum in Taiwan. Although it is not very big, the museum shows in  detail  the  manufacturing process of fishballs. What kind of fish is suitable to make fishballs? What are the representative fishballs of every area?

name: Yingge Crock Pot
location: No. 95 Chongcing Road, Yingge Township, Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Noodles in a crock pot ﬁrst appeared on Jianshanpu Road and they have since moved to the second ﬂoor food court in Pottery Building (Taoguan) on Chongcing Road. This is as close to a local delicacy as you can ﬁnd in Yingge and it is the perfect treat after exploring the shops on ﬁrst ﬂoor.

name: Laoshu Restaurant
location: 12, Lane 290, Section 3, Xinwu Road, Wulai District, , Xindian Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The highly recommended restaurant by "netizens" does not have a menu. Customers order their food from suggestions given by the owner. Popular dishes include fish head  casserole, fried pork and rock shrimp. Visitors are advised to go to the restaurant in a group because it is easier to order different dishes, which are served in very generous portions.

name: Xindian-style Cuisine
location: 125 Guangming Street Xindian District, Taipei Coun, Xindian Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Guangming Eat Street is located near Bitan. Up and down the road are snack shops. Half-way on the street is a shop that sells oily rice that just about every Xindian citizen recognizes as tasty. The flavorful Guangming brand-name sticky rice is slathered in oil and topped with dried fluffy pork and stirred with a sweet sauce.

name: Banqiao Shitou Meatball
location: No.11, Ln. 410, Sec. 2, Wenhua Rd., ,  220, Taiwan, Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The skin is fried and the meatball has rich inner stuffing: stir-fried pork and bamboo, peanut powder, salad sauce, chili paste and juice made by the owner. Satisfying your stomach!

name: World Soy Milk King
location: No. 284 Yonghe Road Section 2, Yonghe City, Taipei County, Yonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Yonghe-made soy milk is known throughout the isles of Taiwan, with World Soy Milk King has the leading business plan and the mostfame.World Soy Milk King is open 24 hours a day, offering Chinese-style breakfast throughout Taiwan with a twist.

name: Gaosyong (Kaohsiung) Black Wagon Wheels
location: No.16, Jhongsing St., ,  23445, Taiwan, Yonghe Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Black Wagon Wheels refers to a type of Taiwanese snack stand that carries a variety of steamed, boiled and grilled vegetables and meats. Among them are stuffed cabbage, black wagon wheels, and other kinds of boiled tempura-like vegetables just waiting there to tease the hunger of every customer to buy. The broth is made from shaved ﬁsh and large pieces of a large white carrot-like radish...

name: Anna Cafe
location: No.1-17, Zhongyang Rd., ,  253, Taiwan, Shimen Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The owner’s delicate handiwork is seen in the mulicolored windmills that spin with the wind. These handiworks sooth one’s heart. Coﬀee and scenery is a great combinaion.

name: Mountaintop Shop of Salted Fried Pig’s Feet
location: No.25, Fanzikeng, ,  223, Taiwan, Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The ingredient of this dish is taken from Shiding’s black pig’s feet, the texture of which is tender and full of collagen. It is first brewed with soybean sauce, and then steamed to maintain the original juices o the meat. After that, it is fried to give the skin its crispy and yet not greasy taste.

name: Under the Old Tree
location: No.163, Shenkeng St., ,  222, Taiwan, Shenkeng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Located at the entrance of the Old Street, it is one of the oldest tofu restaurants here. A table full of tofu dishes is very aﬀordable and gives a sense of happiness. Sinky Tofu with Pig Intesines and Duck Blood Cakes is the signature dish. It is stewed with a dozen of Chinese herbs for over two hours.

name: Lin's mushroom meat sauce
location: No.344, Xinzhuang Rd., ,  242, Taiwan, Xinzhuang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The sauce is made of pig's fresh hindquarter meat. The meat is pickled, wrapped with a layer of sweet potato starch, and then put into pot to boil. So the gravy is fresh and the meat is tender.

name: Linkou Power Plant popsicles
location: No.139, Xiafu, ,  244, Taiwan, Linkou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The traditional popsicles are sold in Linkou Power Plant with many different flavors, such as rice cake, red bean, taro, Luoshen flower and milk, etc. There is a variety of flavors for choice, all cool to the heart. Many people come from very far places for group purchase. A box contains 60 ice-suckers, but you had better prepare an ice box for the sake of environmental protection.

name: Jinshan Kuo's Almond Cookies Shop
location: No. 77, jinbauli St., ,  208, Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Completely handmade, this cookie shop provides pan-fried peanuts, almonds, sesame, pumpkin candy, coriander rolls, and nougat candy, all of which are all fresh without preservatives.

name: Amei Teahouse
location: No. 20, Shixa Lane, Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The Amei Teahouse is located on Shuqi Road. Its strong Japanese architectural style makes it very eye-catching. In particular, when it is rumored that the teahouse looks like the building of Yubaba in the animated picture Spirited Away of Hayao Miyazak, more and more people want to find out the truth about it.

name: Jiufen Jinzhi Hongzao Rouyuan
location: No. 112 (with meat), No. 63 (vegetarian), Jishan St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productsred vinasse rouyuan, vegetarian red vinasse rouyuanOne of the most famous snacks in Jiufen is red vinasse rouyuan. This is a rouyuan containing chunks of meat marinated and fermented with red vinasse. Jiufen Jinzhi Hongzao Rouyuan is an important reason why red vinasse rouyuan has become so well-known in the Jiufen region.

name: Jiufen Old Noodle Restaurant
location: No. 45, Jishan St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended Productsbeef noodles, wonton noodles, peanut ice creamThe Jiufen Old Noodle Restaurant was established in 1958 Currently, Mr. Shi is the second generation owner. Although it was not the first noodle restaurant ever in the Jiufen region, it was the first to ever serve beef noodles.

name: Rice with Turkey
location: No. 264, Section 2, Zhongyang Road, Tucheng District, , Tucheng Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Huixiang Chiayi Rice with Turkey is different from the shredded turkey rice one usually sees at street stalls because this restaurant cuts the meat into larger chunks to make it more firm and chewy. Homemade sauce is added for an authentic southern taste.

name: Liu Biju Chaozhou Casserole Porridge
location: No. 3, Mingquan Rd., , , Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: There're many different methods to cook porridge; Guangdong porridge and Taiwanese salty congee are the common cuisines for general customers. In recent years, the casserole porridge becomes popular in Banqiao due to the use of Taitung Guanshan Emperor Rice as the main ingredient; particularly, not until the guests make an order, the rice won't be put into the casserole. The rice is cook...

name: Minghong Clam Consommé
location: No.87-3, Wenhua N. Rd., ,  241, Taiwan (R.O.C.), Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Minghong Clam Consommé can be found at the corner of  Wun hua Road . Though a small shop selling only rice vermicelli and stewed pork sauce over rice, the eatery’s sizable sign with a big oyster picture on it  is  hard  to  miss.

name: Granny’s Iron Eggs
location: 135-1 Zhongzheng Road, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Dark Chewy Iron EggsWant to try some special iron eggs? Then you have to come to Tamsui for some of Granny’s iron eggs. Their creator, Granny Yang, ran a buffet and noodle shop. On one occasion she got too busy and over-marinated the eggs , and fortunately, customers could not get off enough. The eggs then became a hot selling item for the past 30 years.

name: Granny’s Plum Juice
location: 135-2 Zhongzheng Road, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: When  it  gets  hot,  have  a  glass  of iced plum juice as it is the best way to quench your thirst. Granny's Plum Juice uses dried plums and they are marinated for three months. After  spice, perilla, rosella tea, and 17 other herbs are added, it is then brewed in a clay pot over a small fire and finally turns into a sweet and sour drink.

name: Yeh’s Wonton Restaurant
location: 177 Zhongzheng Road, Tamsui District, , Tamsui Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Jay Chou’s Favorite WontonThere  is  a  restaurant  in Tamsui  that  offers  a vermicelli  dish  that  is famous throughout China and  Hong  Kong — the "Jay Chou Set". This is Yeh’s Wonton Restaurant, famous for the thin layer and rich fillings of wontons served with omelet strips, laver and other veggies. The soup is refreshing, and the set comes with a tender marinated fried drumstick.

name: Yannick Patisserie
location: 127-5 Malian Road, Wanli District, , Wanli Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Media reports made the desert shop extremely popular,  and  many people have come to the café next to its factory in Wanli for some freshly baked desserts. It's a top pick for an enjoyable afternoon tea while you are in Wanli.

name: Haishan Bakery
location: N o. 2 , Zhonghua  Rd . , ,, Shuangxi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The Haishan Bakery is famous for its “Haishan Agar-Pudding Cake,” where the cake ingredients contain agar, flour and fresh eggs. The strong aromatic egg smell fills the small shop when the fresh cakes come out of the oven. The smooth texture will make one accidently eat the entire cake one bite after another. Persistent on adding no fragrances and seasonings, so that everybody loves it, ...

name: Wang’s Tofu
location: No.85, Shiding E. St., , , Shiding Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Special Recommendations: Tofu Pudding, Roasted Tofu

name: Yuelai Pavilion Restaurant
location: No.56, Sec. 1, Zhongshan Rd., ,  252, Taiwan, Sanzhi Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Yuelai pavilion restaurant provides various kinds of Taiwanese dishes and seafood dishes. Crispy fried ribs and curry taro balls are popular house dishes in the store.

name: Zengji Calamari Stew
location: No 150 Wunhua North Road, Sanchong District, Taipei County, Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: There are in particular two shops that sell Calamari Stew in Sanchong Night Market diagonally across the street Minghong Clam Consommé. The shop is larger thus easy to find. At the present address the owners have 30 years of experience selling the delicacy, along with rice vermicelli and stewed ground pork on rice.

name: Meichun Highway Hotel
location: No.22, Sec. 8, Beiyi Rd., ,  232, Taiwan, Pinglin Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The hotel is next to the Pinglin gate. A simplistic restaurant without a setmenu, it oﬀers simple, family dishes. One can tell the owner the budget and preferred dishes, and she will make a whole table of delicious food.

name: Lobster King
location: No.186, Renhe Rd., ,  228, Taiwan, Gongliao Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Lobsters can be prepared in over a dozen ways, such as steam, with meso or wasabi, to give a few examples. Succulent abalones are also a delicacy not to be missed. Every dish can be customized in the store.

name: Tianding Soup Noodles
location: No.22, Desheng St., ,  247, Taiwan, Luzhou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Tianding Qiezai Noodle Restaurant, located in Miaokou business circle of Luzhou, is operated by its boss, Liao Tianding. It has a history of more than 30 years, and is one of very famous restaurants here. It has a very tall and big red sign discernible from very far. The noodle here will never be cooked too sot, and the noodle soup is always clear, fresh and sweet.

name: Deep-sea squid
location: No 26, Duchuantou St., ,  249, Taiwan, Bali Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: The golden fried big squid is crispy and served with special sauces, mayonnaise and mustard, with a topping of dried bonito flakes. It tastes light and not greasy at all.

name: Jinshan Changyi Pastries Shop
location: No.57, Jinbauli St. ,  208, Taiwan, Jinshan Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Unlike the traditional tastes today, this shop provides a variety of Chinese sweets, curry meat pastries, sweetheart cakes, green bean moon cakes, black bean paste, and pineapple cakes for you to choose from.

name: European Country Café
location: No. 177, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: While this store's Chinese name conveys the atmosphere of a European residence in the countryside, the English name "Babka" is an honorific term for old ladies in Eastern Europe, who are often masters at making delicate desserts, cookies, and cakes.

name: Gojinshan Peanut Brittle
location: No.30, Jishan St., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Peanuts were known to ancient people as the "fruit of longevity", which is a great indication of how rich they are in nutrients. In fact, peanuts contain more than just protein, fat, and carbohydrates. They also contain unsaturated fatty acids, amino acids, vitamin B1 and B2, beta carotene, niacin, and other nutrients.

name: Hua Ji Dragon Phoenix Spring Roll
location: Minsheng St. Entrance, , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsDragon Phoenix Spring Roll, Glutinous Rice SausageHave you been asked what is the most difficult thing when trying to preserve authentic flavors? Some people may say it is the pickiness of customers, some may say it will depend on the determination and dedication of the cook.

name: Hereditary A-Mang’s Sweet Taro Balls
location: No. 41-2, Jishan St., ,  224, Taiwan, Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Not far from the entrance of Jishan Old Street (Jiudaokou) is a small signs which says "Hereditary A-Mang's Sweet Taro Balls". This tiny shop, which seats only about a dozen, played a major role in how the sweet taro ball came to be known as a renowned Jiufen snack.Hereditary A-Mang's Sweet Taro Balls is one of the three oldest sweet taro ball shops in Jiufen.

name: A City of Sadness
location: 2F, No.35, Shuqi Rd., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsOld fashioned rice with pork fat, Taiwanese family style stir-fry, economical a la carte, Western set meal, coffeeThe film "A City of Sadness" promoted the beauty of Jiufen globally; hence for a long time, Jiufen and the City of Sadness were virtually synonymous.

name: LiYi Cake Store
location: No.18, Qiche Rd., , , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Recommended ProductsButter sun cake, pineapple cake, curry cake , taro cakePineapple cakes are one of the most renowned and representative snacks in Taiwan. Now only are they well-liked by all ages, in recent years they have become the top gift choice for those traveling abroad.

name: Shijiang Wenzhou Wontons
location: No. 58 Wenhua Road; Sanxia District, , Sanxia Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Stalls and small restaurants serving many of Taiwan’s favorite snacks have converged around Sanxia Old Street, meaning you can find almost anything you desire, including beloved wontons. Shijiang Wenzhou Wontons is located on Wenhua Road and serves affordable wontons that are about half the size of a fist. Only top ingredients are used so when you bite in, you get a huge taste of meat.

name: Kueishan Power Station Popsicles
location: No. 37 Guishan Road, Xindian District, , Xindian Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Kueishan Power Station Ice Pops is a popsicle store located in the water conservation area of the Feitsui Reservoir. Its popsicles attract many tourists who visit just for the sake of having this traditional treat. There are many flavors to try, including pineapple, peanut, milk, and red bean, and their low cost means you can keep coming back for more of this cool, refreshing snack.

name: Traditional Pork Chop and Rice
location: No.85, Yuying St., ,  239, Taiwan, Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Many great foods line Yingge Old Street, such as traditional tofu pudding. But if you are looking for something to fill you up at lunch, one of your best options is at a restaurant serving traditional pork chop and rice. Here the flour added when making the fried pork chop is the perfect amount, creating a crisp exterior to go with the tender meat inside.

name: Yingge Oyster Vermicelli
location: No. 91, Zhongzheng First Road, Yingge District, , Yingge Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Yingge is a place known for being humble, a characteristic reflected in its cuisine. Nearly everywhere you look you can find somewhere serving inexpensive, excellent meals, one example of which is a place simply called Yingge Oyster Vermicelli. When you order these noodles the first thing you notice is that the chef crams lots of ingredients into a small bowl.

name: The Eatery
location: 1st Floor, No. 1 Section, Wenhua 3rd Road, Linkou District, , Linkou Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Enjoy simple and delicious everyday comfort food at our all-day dining restaurant.  We serve up all the local specialty dishes, a range of popular international choices and a tempting dessert selection.

name: Ruifang Food Court
location: No. 2, Lane, 35, Minsheng St., Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Ruifang Food Court is situated across from Ruifang Train Station; located in a traffic hub, it is close to the historical Ruifang Old Street and is a major tourist attraction. The Food Court has been established for more than five decades and has been transformed from a traditional wet market to today’s renowned Food Court. If you are looking for the most authentic Ruifang street eats, y...

name: Misty Cake
location: No. 6-1, Sec. 1, Mingdeng Rd., Ruifang District, , Ruifang Dist., New Taipei City Taiwán, R.O.C
services: Brand Story: Jinguashih in Ruifang was once a major gold mining town. At that time, impoverished miners would have sweet potatoes as the main food to satisfy their hunger. Over the years, the plain and pure flavor has slowly been forgotten by most people. As an effort to rediscover that authentic texture, Misty Cake is borrowing the old-time cooking method and using a puff pastry to wrap...
